CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "My, My! - These damsels indulge in one of woman's favorite pasttimes at the Alpha picnic: "Talk." But this doesn't last long, for there were too many other things to keep them busy."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four women, including two wearing gingham dresses, and one on right wearing saddle shoes, gathered around picnic table at North Park for Alpha Phi Alpha picnic
